🍼 Baby Shopping in Bangkok: What I Found & Loved 🇹🇭

If you’re in Bangkok with a little one, these are some great baby brands and finds I came across that are worth checking out:

✨ Baby Einstein – Fun, interactive educational toys that keep babies engaged.

🪂 BabyBjörn – Their iconic bouncer is a must-have. Easy to fold and carry. Not available in India yet! 

👗 Enfant – Great for comfy occasionwear and everyday sets.

🎀 Miki House – Luxe Japanese label. Pricey, but perfect for weddings, birthdays & photo ops.

🌸 Petit Pie – The best fabrics, amazing blankets and perfect for gifting or celebrations.

🌿 PlanToys – Wooden toys with beautiful design and great quality.

🧼 Nappi Baby – Loved their bamboo swaddles, towels, and muslins.

🎠 Akarana Baby – They have the cutest baby carousels. Saw them at Central Chidlom. 

🍼 Little Palmerhaus – Breast milk storage bags in fun prints and sizes — super cute and practical.

—

🍴 Food Finds for Baby

Bangkok also has an amazing range of baby-friendly food brands! A few I came across:

🍘 Apple Monkey
🥣 Peachy
🧃 Bubs Organic
🍎 Little Étoile Organic

I found most of these brands at Central across the city.
